    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: inference.GRPCInferenceService/ModelInfer<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (Optional TLS)<br/>Protobuf: ModelInferRequest
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: ModelInferResponse<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (Optional TLS)
    Note over RestProxy: Custom marshaler converts<br/>tensor response to JSON<br/>including multi-dimensional<br/>arrays and base64 bytes
    RestProxy-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>RestProxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: inference.GRPCInferenceService/ModelMetadata<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (Optional TLS)
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: ModelMetadataResponse
    RestProxy-->>Client: JSON Model Metadata<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 3: Versioned Inference Request

    Client->>RestProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/versions/{ver}/infer<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (Optional TLS)
